  "time_ut": 1658144780,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd6\u0dc0 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dba\u0dda \u0d85\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd \u0dc3\u0dd3.\u0dc3\u0dd3.\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dba\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd\u0d9c\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An order to give the raw video of the Polduwa protest to the CCD",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Additional Magistrate Harshana Kekunawala ordered the heads of electronic media today (18) to hand over the footage related to the struggle that took place on the 13th at the Polduwa intersection leading to Parliament to the Colombo Crime Division.",
        "The Magistrate issued the orders in consideration of a request made by the Colombo Crimes Division in connection with the incident in which two army personnel were seriously injured during the protest and two ammunition magazines with 30 live rounds and two T56 firearms went missing.",
        "Colombo said that the investigation was initiated in connection with an incident in which two army soldiers were attacked and injured while being members of an illegal meeting on the road from the Polduwa intersection leading to the Parliament to the speaker's official residence and robbed of two ammunition bags with 30 rounds of live ammunition and two T56 type automatic firearms. The crime division had reported the matter to the court.",
        "Accordingly, the Colombo Crimes Division has requested the court to issue an order to provide the unedited videos recorded by the television channels at that time in relation to this investigation."
      ],
